<p>'I’m so excited for this collaboration with Coach,' Jennifer said in a statement at the time.</p>

<p>'It is a timeless brand that I’ve always been a fan of and the upcoming collection really speaks to my personal style - an uptown downtown mix.'</p>

<p>'Jennifer is so authentic. She’s determined and she’s an original who has followed her own path to do things her own way - she really embodies the attitude of Coach and our new campaign,' Creative Director Stuart Vevers said. </p>

